import sys

N, K = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split()))
open = [False for i in range(N + 1)]
count = 0

for i in range(K):
 line = sys.stdin.readline().split()
 if len(line) == 1:
  count = 0
  open = [False for i in range(N + 1)]
 else:
  action, num = line
  num = int(num)
  if open[num]:
   count -= 1
  else:
   count += 1
  open[num] = not open[num]
 print(count)
